"{\"uid\": \"havanatimes.org-diaries-kamil-kenders-an-olympic-return-trip\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Kamil Kenders HAVANA TIMES - Now back in my Havana, and recovered from an exhausting trip, I can detail how difficult it was to return from Bayamo, Granma.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\", \"score\": 0.9707381090555921, \"rank\": 0.030143959787243546, \"text\": \"Kamil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\"}, {\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"score\": 0.9999999997310169, \"rank\": 2.0252751921058663e-10, \"text\": \"Havana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\"}, {\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Granma_Province\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.403534776025554e-13, \"text\": \"Granma\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Granma_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Granma_Province\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HAVANA\", \"from\": 17, \"to\": 23}, {\"ngram\": \"an exhausting trip\", \"from\": 74, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"Bayamo\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Considering that interprovincial transportation gets worse during vacations, I can still say that the mafia that exists to obtain a ticket is immense.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that interprovincial transportation\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 209}, {\"ngram\": \"vacations\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"the mafia\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First attempt at a ticket: Failed.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We dismissed the normal route because there is no point in trying to get a ticket through the app created for it.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the normal route\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"no point\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first mafia begins there when you see that there is space on a bus, and in less than a minute, there are no more seats.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first mafia\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"a bus\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"less than a minute\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 560}, {\"ngram\": \"no more seats\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why does this happen?\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's because there are people buying up the tickets at the established price (a little over 200 pesos) to then resell them for over 3,000 pesos.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the tickets\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"the established price\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"a little over 200 pesos\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"over 3,000 pesos\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attempt number 2: Outside the Bayamo bus terminal (like in all provinces), there are\\\"bukenkes\\\"(those are the people who shout out the destinations of the buses and cars outside the establishment).\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Bayamo bus terminal\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"all provinces\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"the destinations\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"the buses\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"the establishment\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The price of these tickets ranges between 4,500, 5,000, and 6,000 pesos, depending on the size, type of bus, distance, and comfort.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The price\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"these tickets\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"6,000 pesos\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"type\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"bus\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"distance\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thebukenkeshave some sort of arrangements with the bus drivers, so each one of them, with every ticket, gets a good slice of that money.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some sort\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"arrangements\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"the bus drivers\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"every ticket\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"a good slice\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"that money\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In summary, it took me two days to leave Bayamo and return to Havana on a bus with decent conditions.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"score\": 0.9999999997310169, \"rank\": 2.0252751921058663e-10, \"text\": \"Havana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"summary\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"Bayamo\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"a bus\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"decent conditions\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I left on a Sunday at five in the afternoon and arrived in Havana the next day, twelve hours later, which is how long it takes for a bus to cover 840 km.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"score\": 0.9999999997310169, \"rank\": 2.0252751921058663e-10, \"text\": \"Havana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Sunday\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"the afternoon\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"a bus\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"840 km\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was left wanting to return to Bayamo, but it will not be for a long time because, honestly, a lot, a lot of money is needed just for transportation, plus the stress caused by the uncertainty of whether you will be able to travel or not.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bayamo\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"transportation\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"the stress\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"the uncertainty\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more from the diary of Kamil Kenders 